{{Otheruses|Amber}}
'''Amber''' was the name of a [[Thumper (creature)|thumper]] caught by [[Biggs Darklighter/Legends|Biggs Darklighter]] on [[Yavin 4/Legends|Yavin 4]]. He named it after his [[Amber (bodyguard)|bodyguard]] on [[Aquilae (The Star Wars)|Aquilae]]. Amber was killed in the [[Lars treehouse]] after a group of [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] discovered the structure and investigated. When Biggs and [[C-3PO/Legends|Threepio]] hid, Amber attempted to defend them and one of the troopers killed him with his [[Lightsaber/Legends|lazersword]]. Biggs was captured, and taken to a waiting [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[air tank]].<ref name="The Star Wars rough draft">[[The Star Wars rough draft]]</ref>

